const QA=[\
\{id:"A1",text:"My brother's name is Marcus. We live together in New York City. Our apartment is in a nice neighbourhood. There are lots of good restaurants nearby. He is a student at the university. He studies history. He wants to be a professor. He is very busy, but we usually eat out every night. We like to try different food."\},\
\{id:"A2",text:"Gyms are places people go to exercise. At most gyms, you have to pay to be a member. Once you are a member of a gym, you can go as often as you like. Most gyms have exercise machines and weights. Some gyms even have swimming pools and basketball courts. Many gyms offer fitness classes to their members."\},\
\{id:"A3",text:"Anna's closet is very messy and disorganized. She has a hard time finding things in it. Last week, she spent two whole days sorting through everything and organizing the closet. She found a lot of old clothes and shoes that she hadn't worn for years. She gave some of the old things to her sister and the others she donated to a charity."\},\
\{id:"A4",text:"When Lisa came home from work, she found a kitten in front of her door. He was very scared and skinny. So, Lisa took him inside and gave him some food and water. The kitten followed her around all night. Then, he fell asleep on her floor. In the morning, a woman knocked on her door. It was the owner of the kitten."\},\
\{id:"A5",text:"After many years at the same job, some people need a change. A worker can move to a new field or start a business. There are many things to consider when making a change. One thing is education. Some career changes require more education. Another thing to consider is money. It can be hard to accept a lower salary at a new job."\},\
\{id:"A6",text:"Salads are delicious. They are also healthy. It is easy to make a salad. You can make a salad with only lettuce and tomatoes. Good tomatoes are very red. You should wash them in water first and you want to use a sharp knife to cut them. Salads taste very good with dressing. You can put the dressing on top of the salad or on the side."\},\
\{id:"A7",text:"Exercise is very good for your body. It is important to be active every day. There are many ways to exercise. You can walk, run, or play a sport. After a work out, many people feel happy and relaxed. They are usually very healthy. People who work out do not get sick often. They also sleep better because they fall asleep quickly and wake up rested."\},\
\{id:"A8",text:"Many people like to watch movies in theaters. They buy tickets. Then, they buy snacks and drinks. In the theater, they find seats. During the movie, the lights are off. It is very dark. People do not talk. They are very quiet. After the movie, people like to talk about it. They talk about what they liked and didn't like."\},\
\{id:"A9",text:"People have been playing the game of chess for hundreds of years. When playing chess, two players take turns moving their pieces on the board. If a player's piece lands on one of the other person's pieces, it is no longer in the game. Each player has a piece called the king. The game is over when a player loses the king."\},\
\{id:"A10",text:"Many people experience culture shock. It happens when you move to a new and different culture. You have to make a lot of changes and you may feel nervous and confused. You have to meet many new people. Often times you must learn a new language. It is a very natural feeling and usually it does not last long."\},\
\{id:"A11",text:"Instead of living in houses or apartment buildings, some people live on boats. In some cities, this is very common. The boats that people live on are called houseboats. Some of them are a lot like normal boats. They move around and can travel to new places. Other houseboats are more like normal houses. They are always in the same place."\},\
\{id:"A12",text:"With the help of technology, we are able to predict the weather. Before technology, people had to use other means. Some people used cows. They thought that if a cow is lying down, it will rain within twelve hours. Before it rains, the air pressure changes and becomes lower. Cows may feel pain in their joints because of the change."\},\
\{id:"A13",text:"My family bought a new house. It has four bedrooms. Each bedroom has a big closet and two large windows. My bedroom is next to the living room. There is a garden behind the house. I want to grow vegetables in the summer. My parents love the big kitchen. They like to cook for family and friends."\},\
\{id:"A14",text:"Mali, officially called the Republic of Mali, is a country in West Africa. It is bordered on all sides by other countries. There is no access to the sea. There is a desert in the northern part and it is very flat. In general, the southern part has tropical weather while the north is quite dry. The official language in Mali is French."\},\
\{id:"A15",text:"A lot of people use email to communicate. There are many benefits to using email. First, it is very fast. When you send an email, it can travel across the world in seconds. Second, it is good for the environment because paper is saved. Also, the fuel needed to deliver paper mail is saved. Finally, it is very easy to use."\},\
\{id:"A16",text:"Chocolate is a very popular sweet treat enjoyed by people all around the world. It is made from the seeds of a fruit that are processed in a special way and then roasted. Adding milk gives chocolate a creamy texture. Sugar is added to make chocolate taste sweet. Some people like chocolate that isn't very sweet. It's called dark chocolate."\},\
\{id:"A17",text:"Tennis is a popular sport. It is fun to watch and fun to play. It is also great exercise. You can play tennis with a friend or with a few friends. Both men and women like to play tennis. The game has no time limit, so games can sometimes last for hours. It is hard to find a good tennis court, but you can play it on the grass."\},\
\{id:"A18",text:"Many people do not like public speaking. They are afraid to speak in front of a large group of people. There are many ways to get better at public speaking. First, it is good to know the room. You should know where to stand and where to set up your computer. Second, it is important to know your audience."\},\
\{id:"A19",text:"It is never late to learn a language. You can start at any age. There are many reasons to study a new language. Maybe you want to speak with your family or friends. Maybe you want to study abroad. Or maybe you just want to travel. Some people study a language because they like the way it sounds."\},\
\{id:"A20",text:"Most people work during the day. Some people have jobs that require them to work at night. They sleep during the day. They go to bed when the sun rises. They wake up when the sun sets. This isn't always easy. Some people have trouble sleeping when the sun is out."\},\
\{id:"A21",text:"Birthday cakes are served on a person's birthday. The cake is decorated with the words Happy Birthday and the person's name. It is a tradition to put one candle for each year that the birthday person is celebrating. After the candles are lit, family members and friends sing Happy Birthday."\},\
\{id:"A22",text:"Bookstores sell books, magazines, newspapers, calendars, and stationery. Large bookstores have a separate section for children. The bookcases in the children's section are shorter so children can reach the books. Books in bookstores are categorized by subjects. Best-selling books are usually displayed in the front of the store."\},\
\{id:"A23",text:"Bread has been an important part of people's diets since ancient times. The first bread was made of crushed grains and water thousands of years ago. People baked the dough on hot stones, resulting in flat bread. Later, after people learned how to make bread rise, they constructed ovens. Since then, people have enjoyed many varieties of bread."\},\
\{id:"A24",text:"A blog is an online website that is like a diary or journal. The word blog is formed by mixing the two words web and log. Many people like to write blogs. They use them to share their thoughts on topics that they care about. A blog can have text, images, and links to other websites."\},\
\{id:"A25",text:"Traveling by plane is more comfortable than it used to be. In the past, flights were long and bumpy. Today, designers are improving the flying experience. Even though the seats are closer together, the ride is much smoother and quieter. The inside of some planes has changed too. The ceilings are higher. Windows are larger."\},\
\{id:"A26",text:"Many people travel to Iceland to see the northern lights. Some people stay in small huts made out of glass. In these huts, people can easily see the brilliant light displays when the night sky is painted with bright greens, reds, pinks, and purples. The northern lights can be seen from other places too."\},\
\{id:"A27",text:"Typically a public library can be used by anyone. Many countries have public libraries. They are different from other libraries such as those at schools or hospitals. Usually anyone can check out books if they have a library card. Some libraries also provide free internet. On weekends, many parents take their children to the library."\},\
\{id:"A28",text:"Many studies have shown that having a large group of friends boosts your happiness and health. Friendships may even add years to your life. Not having many friends can be a considerable risk to your health. Friends offer encouragement when times are hard."\},\
\{id:"A29",text:"Pizza is a kind of flat bread that is baked in a very hot oven. The base of a pizza is a simple type of bread made of flour, water, salt, and oil. Most of the time it is topped with tomato sauce and cheese, but many things can be put on a pizza. Although pizza was first made in Italy, it is now popular in many parts of the world."\},\
\{id:"A30",text:"More and more people want to grow their own fruits and vegetables. As a result, many people are reading about gardening and even taking classes to learn more. Many people who garden live in suburbs, but people who live in cities can also garden. For example, some people plant gardens on their roofs."\},\
\{id:"A31",text:"A pilot's job is to fly an airplane. Pilots are needed around the world to fly many different types of planes. Only the most experienced pilots work for commercial airlines. Being a pilot can be exciting. Pilots often travel to well-known cities. It is also a big responsibility. Pilots must be able to fly through challenging weather."\},\
\{id:"A32",text:"A waffle is a food that is typically eaten for breakfast. It is made from flour, water, oil, and eggs. Waffles are usually in the shape of a square, but sometimes they can be round. Many people eat them with eggs and orange juice for breakfast. Others like to eat waffles for dessert. They put fresh fruit and cream on top."\},\
\{id:"A33",text:"Washington is a state in the far northwest part of the United States. There are mountains in the middle, so it is usually wet in the west and dry in the east. This makes it good for growing many things, such as cherries, apples and pears. There are many trees, so Washington exports a lot of wood to the rest of the world."\},\
\{id:"A34",text:"New York City is known as the city that never sleeps. That's because the people in this huge urban area seem to be on the go day and night. Trains rumble into stations from dawn to dusk. If you're unlucky enough to live by one of the above-ground trains, you'll probably need to wear earplugs to sleep."\},\
\{id:"A35",text:"People have been creating maps for thousands of years. Long ago, explorers went around the world and created drawings showing where they had been. Over time, maps got more and more detailed. Maps help us learn about a specific area. We may use a map to figure out which roads to take to get to a new place."\},\
\{id:"A36",text:"As people get older, it can become harder to remember things. Some research shows that there are ways to prevent memory loss. The first is to eat right and get plenty of exercise. Second, it is important to exercise your mind. This can be done by learning new things. Living a life without a lot of stress is also important."\},\
\{id:"A37",text:"It can be hard to grow crops in dry climates. When there is not a lot of water, it is important to avoid wasting it. Farmers can do a variety of things to make sure that their plants get enough water. They can water the plants at night when it's cooler. They can also cover the ground with mulch."\},\
\{id:"A38",text:"Please see the updated course information and reading material that are attached to this message. All students are requested to bring their handouts to every class. The teacher will be bringing a projector, and the classroom is equipped with a screen. Also, remember that there will be an optional film showing after the first class."\},\
\{id:"A39",text:"Organizations grow or fail according to the effectiveness of their meetings. Group leaders should prepare topics for discussion beforehand. During the meeting, the leader should guide the group in making decisions and assigning follow up tasks. Finally, it's important that all members receive a copy of accurate notes of what was discussed at the meeting."\}\
];\
