\{id:"H1",passage:"As most of you know, tonight and tomorrow we will be replacing the carpet in the lobby. As a result, the office will be closed tomorrow morning until noon. Please work from home until then, and come to the office in the afternoon. Thanks.",model:"We are replacing the carpet in the lobby tonight and tomorrow. Therefore, the office will be closed tomorrow morning. Please work from home and come to the office in the afternoon."\},\
\{id:"H2",passage:"Sarah's shower is broken. She called a repairman to come and fix it, but he never showed up. She called another repairman, but he isn't available until next week. Sarah will have to use her neighbor's shower until next week.",model:"Sarah's shower is broken, so she called a repairman. The first one didn't show up, and the second one is busy until next week. Sarah has to use her neighbor's shower for now."\},\
\{id:"H3",passage:"Sam has been living in the same apartment building for many years. He loves the quiet neighborhood. One day, a new neighbor moved in across the hall. The neighbor played the piano for several hours every evening. Sam was very bothered by all of the noise. Finally, he asked his neighbor to play the piano while Sam wasn't at home. The neighbor agreed.",model:"Sam lives in a quiet apartment, but his new neighbor played the piano every night. Sam was very bothered by the noise. Finally, the neighbor agreed to play only when Sam was at work."\},\
\{id:"H4",passage:"Joseph's parents took a trip. Their house is full of plants, so they asked him to water their plants while they were away. Joseph got very busy. He forgot to water the plants. When his parents came back, all of the plants had died.",model:"Joseph's parents went on a trip. They asked him to water the plants. Joseph was busy and forgot. All the plants died."\},\
\{id:"H5",passage:"Andrea loves to cook. She wants to write a cookbook with all her favorite recipes. So, she makes dinner every night for her family. After dinner, she asks what they think of the food. Then, she decides if she wants to include the recipe in her cookbook or not.",model:"Andrea loves to cook and wants to write a cookbook. She cooks for her family every night and asks for their feedback to decide which recipes to include."\},\
\{id:"H6",passage:"David had an exam the next day. So, he stayed up very late studying. In the morning, his alarm went off, but David knocked the alarm to the floor and it broke. Then, David fell asleep again. When he woke up, he had slept well, but he had missed the exam.",model:"David had an exam. He stayed up late to study. In the morning, he broke his alarm clock and fell asleep again. He missed the exam."\},\
\{id:"H7",passage:"When Lisa came home from work, she found a kitten in front of her door. He was very scared and skinny. So, Lisa took him inside and gave him some food and water. The kitten followed her around all night. In the morning, a woman knocked on her door \'97 it was the owner. Lisa gave the kitten back but was very sad to see him go.",model:"Lisa found a thin kitten at her door. She gave it food and water. The next day, the owner came. Lisa gave the kitten back but felt sad."\},\
\{id:"H8",passage:"Richard is looking for an apartment to rent. He has been looking for many months, but he cannot find anything in his price range. One day, a friend calls him. She tells him that she is moving and thought he might be interested in her apartment. The rent is in his price range, so Richard calls the landlord. The landlord agrees to rent the apartment to Richard.",model:"Richard wanted a cheap apartment. His friend was moving out and told him about her place. The rent was good. Richard called the landlord and got it."\},\
\{id:"H9",passage:"Marie owns a restaurant. One night, all of her servers called her and said they were too sick to work. It was a holiday, so Marie knew that it would be a busy night. She called her parents and asked if they could help and work that night. They agreed and did a good job.",model:"Marie owns a restaurant. One night, all her workers were sick. She asked her parents to help. They did a great job."\},\
\{id:"H10",passage:"A young couple took a trip to China. They asked their friend to take care of their cats while they were away. The friend stayed at their house during the trip. He took care of the cats, but also ate all of the couple's food. When the couple came back, they didn't have any food left, but their cats were happy.",model:"A couple went to China. Their friend looked after their cats at their house. He fed the cats but ate all the couple's food."\},\
\{id:"H11",passage:"Please join us next Wednesday evening for a talk by our new college president. The talk is free and will be held in the main auditorium. Topics include rising tuition, class sizes, and parking. Please come prepared with questions!",model:"The college president will give a talk next Wednesday. It is free and in the auditorium. Topics include tuition and parking. Please bring questions."\}\
];\
